hadiths[42]{hadithnumber,text}:
3120,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do chitkabrey aur seengon waley mendhon ki qurbani diya kartey they, aur (zibeh kartey waqt) Bismillah aur takbir padhtey they. mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko , un ki gardan par qadam Mubarak rakh kar apney haath sey unhen zibeh kartey dekha."
3121,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eid key din do mendhey qurban kiye. jab unhen qibla rukh kya to farmaya : (إِنِّي وَجَّهْتُ وَجْهِيَ لِلَّذِي فَطَرَ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضَ حَنِيفًا وَمَا أَنَا مِنَ الْمُشْرِكِينَ إِنَّ صَلَاتِي وَنُسُكِي وَمَحْيَايَ وَمَمَاتِي لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ وَبِذَلِكَ أُمِرْتُ وَأَنَا أَوَّلُ الْمُسْلِمِين اللهم منك ولك an محمد و امته) mainey yaksu ho kar apna chehra us Allah ki taraf kar liya jisney aasmano aur zamin ko paida kya aur main mushrekin mein sey nahin . beshak meri namaz , meri qurbani, meri zindagi aur meri maut Allah key liye hai jo sarey jahano ka Malik hai, uska koi shareek nahin. mujhey isi baat ka hukm diya gaya hai aur main sab sey pehla farman-bardar hun. aey Allah! ye janwer tujhi sey mila aur terey hi liye qurban kya. Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur un ki ummat ki taraf sey ."
3122,"Hazrat Aaisha aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab qurbani karna chahtey to do badey badey, motey tazey, seengon waley, chitkabrey aur khassi mendhey khareedtey . eik apni ummat ki taraf sey zibeh farmatey, yani ummat key har us fard ki taraf sey jo Allah ki tohid ki gawahi deta ho aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key pegham pahunchaney (aur Rasool honey) ki gawahi deta ho. aur doosra Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey , aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aal ki taraf sey zibeh kartey."
3123,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas ( qurbani karney ki) gunjaaish ho aur wo qurbani na karey to usey chahiye ke hamari eid gaah key qarib bhi na aaye ."
3124,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey puchha ke kya qurbani wajib hai? unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani ki aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad musalman qurbani detey rahey aur yehi tariqa jari hai. Hazrat jabla bin Sahim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey yehi sawal kya aur unhoney yehi jawab diya."
3125,"Hazrat Mikhnaf bin Sulem (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Arfa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qarib thehrey huye they. aap ney farmaya : logo! har ghar walon par har saal qurbani aur Ateera (wajib) hai. kya tumhen malum hai ke Ateera kya hai? wohi jisey log Rajbiya kehtey hain."
3126,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qurbani key din Adam ka beta koi aisa amal nahin karta jo Allah ko khoon bahaney (janwer ki qurbani kerney) sey ziyada mehbub ho. wo (janwer) qiyamat key din apney seengon, khuron aur baalon samet aayega (aur neki key paldey mein rakha jaeyga. qurbani key janwer ka) khoon zamin par girney sey pehley Allah key yahan (qubuliyat ka) maqam hasil kar leta hai, isliye khush dili sey qurbani kya karo."
3127,Hazrat Zed bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key as-haab Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! ye qurbaniyan kya hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey baap Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki sunnat hain. unhoney kaha : is mein hamarey liye kya (sawab) hai? aap ney farmaya : har baal key badley neki hai. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! aur oon? farmaya : oon key bhi har baal key badley neki hai.
3128,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney seengon waley nar mendhey ki qurbani di. wo siyahi khata, siyahi mein chalta aur siyahi mein dekhta tha."
3129,"Hazrat Yunus bin Maisra bin Halbas (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sabab Hazrat abu-Saeed Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) key sath qurbani key janwer kharidney gaya . Yunus bin maisraa bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aisey mendhey ki taraf ishara kya jis key kanon aur galey ka kuch hissa siyah tha. wo jismani tor par na ziyada ooncha tha na ziyada past tha. unhoney farmaya : merey liye ye kharid lo. goya unhoney usey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key mendhey key mushabeh qarar diya."
3130,"Hazrat abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen kafan wo hai jo eik rang ki do chaadaron par mushtamil ho aur behtareen qurbani seengon wala mendha hai."
3131,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log eik safar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke eidul-azhaa aa gaee , chunanche hamney das das aadmiyon ki taraf sey eik eik oont aur saat saat aadmiyon ki taraf sey eik eik gaey mushtarka tor par zibeh ki."
3132,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Hudebiya mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik oont saat afrad ki taraf sey aur eik gaey saat afrad ki taraf sey zibeh ki."
3133,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hajjatul-wadaa main apni un azwaaj ki taraf sey, jinhoney Umra ada kya tha, mushtarka tor par eik gaey zibeh ki."
3134,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein (eik baar) oonton ki qillat ho gaee to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gaayon ko qurban karney ka hukm dey diya."
3135,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hajjatul-wadaa mein aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf sey eik gaey zibeh ki.
3136,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : merey zimmey eik oont hai (mainey usey zibeh karney ki nazar maana hai) aur main (maali tor par) uski taqat bhi rakhta hun lekin mujhey wo milta nahin ke kharid lun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey hukm diya ke saat bakriyan kharid kar zibeh kar dey.
3137,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Tahaama key ilaqey mein Zul-Hulefa key maqam par they. hamen (ghanimat mein) oont aur bakriyan milin. logon ney jaldi ki. (yani) hamney (ghanimat) taqseem honey sey pehley ( janwer zibeh kar key) degen pakka lin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur aap key hukm sey un (degon) ko ulta diya gaya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik oont das bakriyon key barabar qarar diya (aur uskey mutabiq maale-ghanimat key janwer taqseem kiye .)"
3138,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen kuch bakriyan din jo unhoney qurbani key liye ( Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey) Sahaba kiram mein taqseem kar din. (un key paas) bakri ka eik saala bacha (baqi) reh gaya . unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar di to aap ney farmaya : uski qurbani tum dey do.
3139,Hazrat Umme Bilal bint Hilal Rahimahullah ney apney walid sey riwayat ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bhed key Juzaa ki qurbani jayez hai.
3140,"Hazrat Aasim bin Kalib (Rahimahullah) ney apney walid (Hazrat Kalib bin Shahab (Rahimahullah)) sey riwayat ki, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi key sath they jinka naam Hazrat Majaashe (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) tha jo ke qabila banu Sulem mein sey they. (qurbani key liye) bakriyan (taqseem ki gaeen to) kam pad gaeen, chunanche unhoney eik shakhs ko hukm diya to usney aelan kya ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : bilashuba eik saala, do daante ki jagah kifaayat kar jata hai."
3141,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do daante key siwa koi janwer ( qurbani mein) zibeh na karo, siwaye uskey ke tumharey liye (do daanta janwer talash karna) mushkil ho jaey to bhed ka ek sala bachcha zibeh kar do ."
3142,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us janwer ko zibeh karney sey mana farmaya hai jis ka kaan aagey sey kataa huwa ho, ya jiska kaan peechey sey kataa huwa ho, ya jiska kaan chira huwa ho, ya jis key kaan mein (gol) surakh ho, ya uska hont kata huwa ho."
3143,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamen Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke hum (qurbani key janwer ki) aankhen aur kaan achi tarah dekh liya karen."
3144,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Feeroz (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mujhey bataaiye ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani key kis janwer ko napasand kya hai ya us sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney haath sey is tarah ishara kya. aur mera haath Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key haath sey kotaah hai. (aur farmaya :) qurbani mein chaar janwer jayez nahin : wo kaana janwer jiska kaana pan wazeh ho, bimar janwer jiski bimari wazeh ho, langda janwer jiska langdapan zahir ho aur dublaa janwer jiski haddiyon mein gooda na ho. Ubaid ney kaha : main to pasand nahin karta ke uskey kaan mein naqs ho. Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jo chiz tumhen pasand nahin, usey chhod do lekin usey kisi par haram na karo."
3145,Hazrat Ali sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us janwer ki qurbani deney sey mana farmaya jiska seeng toota huwa ya kaan kata huwa ho.
3146,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney qurbani key liye eik mendha kharida. bhediya uskey sirinon (chootdon) aur kaan sey kuch hissa kaat kar ley gaya. hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey masla daryaft kya to aap ney hamen hukm diya ke uski qurbani kar den."
3147,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey sawal kya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak main tum logon mein qurbaaniyaan kis tarah hoti thin ? unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamana Mubarak mein aadmi apni taraf sey aur apney ghar walon ki taraf sey eik bakri ki qurbani kar diya karta tha. (us mein sey) wo khud bhi khatey , aur dusron ko bhi khilatey . baad mein log fakhr ( key tor par ziyada janwer zibeh) karney lagey to wo haal ho gaya jo aap (aaj kal) dekh rahey hain."
3148,"Hazrat abu-Sareeha (Huzaifa bin Usaid ghifaari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey ghar walon ney mujhey ghalat kaam par majbur kar diya jabkey mujhey sunnat tariqa malum hai eik ghar waley eik bakri ya do bakriyan zibeh kya kartey they. ab to (agar hum eik bakri ki qurbani den to) hamarey hamsaaey hamen bakheel kehney lagtey hain."
3149,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab zul-hijja ka ( pehla) ashra shuru ho jaey aur tum mein sey koi qurbani karney ka irada rakhta ho to usey chahiye ke apney baalon ya apni jald sey kisi chiz ko haath na lagaey."
3150,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs zul-hijja ka chaand dekh ley aur uska irada qurbani karney ka ho to wo apney baalon aur naakhunon (ko kaatney) key qarib bhi na jaey."
3151,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney qurbani key din namaz sey pehley ( qurbani ka janwer) zibeh kar diya . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey hukm diya ke wo dobara (qurbani) kerey.
3152,"Hazrat Jundub (bin Abdullah) Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz eidul-Azha mein hazir huwa. kuch logon ney namaz sey pehley (janwer) zibeh kar liye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey jisney namaz sey pehley (janwer) zibeh kya, wo dobara qurbani kerey. aur jisney (pehley zibeh) nahin kya, wo Allah ka naam ley kar zibeh kerey."
3153,"Hazrat Uwemir bin Ashqar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney namaz sey pehley (qurbani ka janwer) zibeh kar liya , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya to aap ney farmaya : dobara qurbani do ."
3154,"Hazrat abu-Zaid (Amr bin akhtab) Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ansar key eik ghar key paas sey guzrey to aap ko gosht pakney (ya bhunney) ki khushbu mehsus hui . aap ney farmaya : ye kon hai jisney (pehley hi) zibeh kar liya hai? hamara eik (Ansari) aadmi aap ki taraf bahar nikla aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main hun, mainey namaz ( eid ) sey pehley (qurbani ka janwer ) zibeh kar liya tha taake apney ghar walon aur hamsaayon ko khilaaun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey dobara zibeh karney ka hukm diya to usney kaha : qism hai Allah ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin! merey paas to sirf bhed ka eik memna hai. aap ney farmaya : usi ko zibeh kar dey, terey baad kisi ki taraf sey Juzaa (qurban karna) kafi nahin hoga."
3155,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, aap ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke apni qurbani apney haath sey zibeh kar rahey they aur apna qadam Mubarak uski gardan par rakha huwa tha."
3156,Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabila Banu Zuraiq key mohalley ki taraf janey waley raastey par gali key kinarey apni qurbani apney haath sey chhuri key sath zibeh ki.
3157,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke wo aap key (qurbani key) tamam oonton ka gosht, unki khalen aur jhoolen gharibon mein taqseem kar den."
3158,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey har oont ki eik eik boti ley kar handiyaa mein dali gaee (aur pakaai gaee.) tab unhoney ( Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sathiyon ney ) kuch gosht khaya aur kuch shorbaa piya .
3159,"ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qurbani ka gosht sanbhaal rakhney sey logon key faqr o faaqa ki wajeh sey mana farmaya tha, phir ijazat dey di ."
3160,"Hazrat Nabisha (bin Abdullah Hazli) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumko qurbani key gosht teen din sey ziyada rakhney sey mana kya tha. ab khao aur zakhira karo."
3161,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (qurbani) eid gaah mein zibeh kya kartey they.
